name: NAW Britfest 2007 DVD
description: The NAW Britfest 2007 2 DVD set features NAW’s biggest show of the year. Part one features a cruiserweight match for the new title and Sand Dog v Alex McConnell in a last man standing match plus more. Meanwhile part 2 sees Dave Williams go one on one with Napalm and the triple threat main event featuring Dan Legend, Tyrant and Pyro plus much more! This 2 DVD set also comes with bonus material as you get to see the traditional pre Britfest battle royal featuring many past and present NAW personalities!

name: NAW Two Year Anniversary <2 disk>
description: Catch the NAW anniversary weekend in full in this packed two disk DVD set. This weekend made history in NAW as it featured wrestlers from over seas for the first time ever. See them in action aswell as all the other top names in NAW including Tyrant, Pyro, Ashley Dunn, Costa and Steve Farrell. The two Disks feature Collision 15 and 16, Fusion 14, End of Year awards and a bonus match from December 2005 between Steve Farrell and Tyrant.

name: NAW Britfest 2005 DVD
description: This is the historic re launch of NAW, Britfest 2005. Featuring many of the top names in UKBYW history including Steve Farrell, Voodoo, Dan Selby, Danny Dreamer, Awax, Tyrant and more. The DVD set is two disks and features two days of wrestling.

name: NAW Love/Hate 2007
description: NAW Love/Hate 2007 saw Ashley Dunn defend the NAW heavyweight championship against Dave Williams. Meanwhile Pyro and Tyrant went one on one in a grudge match and there was alot on the line as the cousins Steve Farrell and Dan Van Virtigo teamed against Joshua Wall and Mike McKnight. The DVD also features Fusion where Natrix and Napalm defend the NAW tag team titles against Chris Goodwin and Denzel.

name: NAW logo T.shirt
description: This T.shirt is a high quality white or black cotton T.shirt with the NAW logo on the front. Sizes include S,M, L, XL or XXL.
